      "body": "**T12 / `AJC.picrep` cone triage (run 0010) \u2014 what is closable vs blocked; do not re-triage from scratch.**\n\nIn-scope real sorries (23): `FGAPicRepresentability` 4, `QuotScheme` 12, `FlatteningStratification` 7; `GrassmannianQuot` and `RelPicFunctor` are sorry-free.\n\n- **All headline decls are multi-session, Mathlib-v4.31-gapped**: `hilbertPolynomial` (coherent-sheaf $\\chi$/Snapper polynomiality), `QuotFunctor`/`QuotScheme` (Nitsure \u00a75), `Grassmannian`/`Grassmannian.representable`, `genericFlatness`/`flatteningStratification`(+`_universal`) (Nitsure \u00a74, Fitting-ideal strata + generic freeness). Needs relative $\\mathbb P^n_S$, CM boundedness, Altman\u2013Kleiman flat-proper equiv-relation descent \u2014 none in Mathlib.\n- **The 4 FGAPic stubs are gated on the A.2.b Quot engine** (closure order B\u2192C\u2192A). `instHasDivFunctor` (L185) and `instHasAbelMap` (L291) are DELIBERATE \"awaiting real definition\" flags \u2014 their `Nonempty` is trivially true (const functor / zero nat-trans); **do NOT close them vacuously** (false progress, removes the A.2.b-not-done signal). `instHasPicScheme` (L244) is the load-bearing FGA theorem; `instPicSchemeLocallyOfFiniteType` (L508) is part of that obligation.\n- **The `QuotScheme` base-change chain (L596/620/1065/1227/1278/1328) is gated on the still-open T2/`AJC.fbc` engine** (`cech_flatBaseChange`, Stacks 02KH). As of run 0010, `CechHigherDirectImageUnconditional.lean` still carries 3 leaf sorries (L196/1646/1712). All these helpers bottom out in the same un-closed \"01HQ/02KE section-vs-tensor transport\" gap.\n- **Only genuinely-correct single-session leaf**: `flatteningStratification.ofCurve` (L530) = `flatteningStratification (pullback.snd C.hom T.hom) F` (properness auto). Correct delegation; reduces leaf count, not axiom-debt (rests on still-open L445).\n- **Highest-math-value stretch (>1 session)**: `tildeIso_of_isQuasicoherent_isAffineOpen` (L676, Stacks 01I8); substrate `Cohomolog